MASTER_DIRECTORY.summary: The group embarks on a salvage mission, encountering challenges and humorous exchanges as they dismantle a building for valuable items. Grayson and Mike lead the effort, with moments of camaraderie and witty banter, discussing plans to return for more items. Amidst handling equipment and navigating obstacles, they share light-hearted stories and experiences, while dealing with unexpected surprises like hidden cats and quirky machinery.
